<view class="bind-page">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="title">家长监护绑定</view>
    <view class="subtitle">绑定后可查看孩子消费记录并设置监护权限</view>
  </view>

  <view class="form-card">
    <view class="form-item">
      <view class="label">孩子用户ID</view>
      <input
        class="input"
        type="number"
        placeholder="请输入孩子的用户ID"
        value="{{childUserId}}"
        bindinput="onChildUserIdInput"
      />
    </view>

    <view class="form-item">
      <view class="label">验证码</view>
      <view class="code-input-row">
        <input
          class="input code-input"
          type="number"
          placeholder="请输入6位验证码"
          value="{{verifyCode}}"
          bindinput="onVerifyCodeInput"
          maxlength="6"
        />
        <button
          class="send-code-btn {{countdown > 0 ? 'disabled' : ''}}"
          bindtap="onSendCode"
          disabled="{{sending || countdown > 0}}"
        >
          {{countdown > 0 ? countdown + 's后重发' : '发送验证码'}}
        </button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="tips-card">
    <view class="tips-title">温馨提示</view>
    <view class="tips-item">1. 请先让孩子在个人中心查看并告知其用户ID</view>
    <view class="tips-item">2. 验证码将发送到孩子账号，需孩子配合提供</view>
    <view class="tips-item">3. 绑定后您可设置消费限额、一键冻结等功能</view>
  </view>

  <button
    class="bind-btn"
    bindtap="onBind"
    loading="{{submitting}}"
    disabled="{{submitting}}"
  >
    立即绑定
  </button>
</view>
